<li id="cite_note-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5" title="">^</a></b> Harmon-Jones, E.; P. Winkielman (2007). Social Neuroscience: Integrating Biological and Psychological Explanations of Social Behavior. Guilford Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781593854041" class="internal">ISBN 978-1-59385-404-1</a>.</li>
